description:

name: Talla 2XLC - Tranceology 2 - the brandnew Double Artist CD!
description: Talla 2XLC, legendary DJ, Producer and Promoter releases his new Double Artist Album "Tranceology 2" on his american partner label Cleopatra Records. Its comes with 18 mindblowing extended versions and rare mixes of his recent songs.  Special collaborations with a host of top shelf producers including American DJ & host of Tytanium Sessions Sean Tyas. Beatport chart topper Martin Roth, DJ Magazine’s Top 100 DJ John O’Callaghan, Giuseppe Ottaviani, Jerome Isma-e and so many more.

name: !! Technoclub Backpack für Laptop, CDs, Vinyl etc !!
description:
Ultimate Rare Collectors Item! The Technoclub Backpack (Das ultimative rare Fan Item, der Technoclub Rucksack Back pack)

It doesn´t matter if you want to carry a laptop, cds, vinyl or anything else. The Technoclub backpack is awesome to carry everything! It has several pockets on the front and inside. Amazing bag for Travelling too! And it has a regular strap and 2 shoulder straps to carry the bag. 

We only found 5 last bags in our storage room. So be quick and collect this rare item!
